				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The army of the absolute are on their way to Baldur's Gate! The player now has access to Act 3, but they just attempted to head back towards the Act 1 region. Time is short and Daisy makes it clear their is no time to pick berries with druids or drink with goblins. Being stubborn leads to the Thrall of the Absolute game over sequence."
